ike":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:39:39.000Z","msg":"輝夜姫同會長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f093ecf0fd904bbb1b807d9649a499cb25d8a19","tid":2496364,"uid":365058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:39:47.000Z","msg":"安德尊 李錦聯"},{"pid":"04fee5a5d8fdff323bc86c4ed377fa429adda5d0","tid":2496364,"uid":8141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:40:13.000Z","msg":"流川同櫻木<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係當安西教練同櫻木講，要好好觀察流川，然後比佢付出多三倍嘅努力去練習，否則就無辦法喺高中生涯追上佢 嗰度<br />\n比著係平時嘅櫻木已經發晒爛渣，但嗰次好專心咁聽教<br />\n成個宿敵feel真係出晒嚟<br />\n<br />\n悟空同比達我覺得鳥山明始終偏心悟空，永遠高比達半班<br />\n似係戰友多過似宿敵<br />\n<br />\n仲有加旋同布拉哥<br />\n進同瀨那<br />\nL同月"},{"pid":"023249de74fdf40ccbc4678412458f1c1dc9516d","tid":2496364,"uid":154528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:43:00.000Z","msg":"賴那 vs 進"},{"pid":"e357028c05fdc38459573ceca2fcc0bba117e1fa","tid":2496364,"uid":214588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"023249de74fdf40ccbc4678412458f1c1dc9516d","tid":2496364,"uid":154528,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:43:00.000Z","msg":"賴那 vs 進"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:49:02.000Z","msg":"呢啲就真係宿敵啦<br />\n<br />\nSlamdunk兩位男主點都係叫競爭對手啦下話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />宿敵首先要敵對 人哋同team喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4257ab58bbabfdc11e3cd0008ea1c803af576066","tid":2496364,"uid":159997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-19T19:57:25.000Z","msg":"寶少 馬沙"},{"pid":"6596cb172727c0b4c14939ec033ee72938823e81","tid":2496364,"uid":261873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e357028c05fdc38459573ceca2fcc0bba117e1fa","tid":2496364,"uid":214588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"023249de74fdf40ccbc4678412458f1c1dc9516d","tid":2496364,"uid":154528,"like":